---
// Hero principal de la home
---

<section
  class="relative flex items-center justify-center px-6 pt-32 pb-24 overflow-hidden bg-base-bg"
  style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 25% 60%, rgba(138, 179, 220, 0.35), transparent 55%), radial-gradient(circle at 75% 10%, rgba(230, 207, 132, 0.35), transparent 55%);"
>
  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <p
      class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest text-base-ink/60 uppercase mb-4 animate-fade-in-up duration-700"
    >
      Agencia de Marketing Digital
    </p>
    <h1
      class="font-display text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl tracking-tighter font-bold mb-8 text-base-ink animate-fade-in-up duration-700 delay-150"
    >
      Marcas que <span class="relative italic text-base-ink isolate">
        <span
          aria-hidden="true"
          class="absolute inset-x-[-0.08em] bottom-[12%] h-[38%] bg-brand-yellow -rotate-2 rounded-sm -z-10"
        ></span>crecen</span
      ><br />con propósito
    </h1>
    <p
      class="text-lg md:text-xl text-base-ink/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 text-pretty animate-fade-in-up duration-700 delay-300"
    >
      En Zarpa Creativa combinamos estrategia, creatividad y datos para que tu
      marca no solo aparezca, sino que conecte.
    </p>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center animate-fade-in-up duration-700 delay-500"
    >
      <a
        href="/servicios"
        class="inline-block bg-base-ink text-base-bg font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-base-ink/80 transition-colors"
      >
        Nuestros servicios
      </a>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block border border-base-ink/20 text-base-ink font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-base-ink/5 transition-colors"
      >
        Hablemos
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero image -->
    <div
      class="hero-image-wrap mt-16 animate-fade-in-up duration-1000 delay-700"
    >
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514888286974-6c03e2ca1dba?w=1400&q=80"
        alt="Gato mirando a cámara"
        class="hero-img"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-image-wrap {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .hero-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: clamp(260px, 45vw, 560px);
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
</style>
